OL,7,FAlmost 100 victims of the infected
OL,8,Fblood scandal have died in the year
OL,9,Fsince the final recommendations were
OL,10,Fmade on compensation, a charity has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe Infected Blood Inquiry, which is
OL,14,Fdue to publish its final report in
OL,15,FMay, made its final recommendations on
OL,16,Fcompensation for victims and their
OL,17,Floved ones in April 2023.
