OL,7,FHe said that "no time must be wasted
OL,8,Fin delivering redress" as he
OL,9,Frecommended that a compensation scheme
OL,10,Fshould be set up before the final
OL,11,Freport of the inquiry, and run by an
OL,12,Farm's-length body independent of
OL,13,FGovernment.
OL,15,FThe Government has previously been
OL,16,Faccused of dragging its feet over
OL,17,Fcompensation and Prime Minister Rishi
OL,18,FSunak was heckled when he appeared
OL,19,Fbefore the inquiry last year as he
OL,20,Fvowed to pay compensation "as swiftly
OL,21,Fas possible".
