OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"Sir Brian also clearly recommended
OL,8,Fthat the arm's-length body that will
OL,9,Fdeliver the compensation scheme should
OL,10,Fbe set up and running by the end of
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,F"Shamefully, this hasn't happened and
OL,14,Fgovernment continues to fail this
OL,15,Fgroup and prolong their suffering.
OL,16,FWhile in the last year almost 100 more
OL,17,Fvictims of the scandal have died.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
