OL,7,F"Sir Brian has been crystal clear on
OL,8,Fhis recommendations around
OL,9,Fcompensation and these must be
OL,10,Fimmediately acted on when the final
OL,11,Freport is published on May 20. Victims
OL,12,Fhave already suffered for far, far too
OL,13,Flong."
OL,15,FRachel Halford, chief executive of The
OL,16,FHepatitis C Trust, also called for the
OL,17,FGovernment to "immediately establish a
OL,18,Ffull compensation scheme".
