OL,7,FShe added that, despite the inquiry's
OL,8,Frecommendations being laid out a year
OL,9,Fago, the Government has "repeatedly
OL,10,Frefused" to act on them "and still
OL,11,Finsists that it is waiting for the
OL,12,Ffinal report before laying out its
OL,13,Fplans".
OL,15,F"While the Government delays, people
OL,16,Fare dying and uncertainty about the
OL,17,Ffuture is actively harming infected
OL,18,Fblood survivors and their families;
OL,19,Fpeople whose lives have already been
OL,20,Fdevastated by infected blood," Ms
OL,21,FHalford said.
