OL,7,F"The Government must stop dragging its
OL,8,Ffeet and immediately establish a full
OL,9,Fcompensation scheme, and extend
OL,10,Fcompensation to everyone affected,
OL,11,Fincluding people given hepatitis B,
OL,12,Fpeople infected through transfusions
OL,13,Fafter 1991, and every parent who
OL,14,Fwatched their child die as a result of
OL,15,Fthis horrific scandal."
