OL,7,FKate Burt, chief executive of the
OL,8,FHaemophilia Society, said: "Our
OL,9,Fcommunity has watched with increasing
OL,10,Fanger, disbelief and cynicism as the
OL,11,FGovernment blatantly tries to pass the
OL,12,Fbuck on compensation.
OL,14,F"A year after the Infected Blood
OL,15,FInquiry recommended that compensation
OL,16,Fshould be paid, Prime Minister Rishi
OL,17,FSunak's refusal to accept
OL,18,Fresponsibility on this issue is
OL,19,Frepugnant and cruel.
