OL,7,F"In just a few weeks, the Infected
OL,8,FBlood Inquiry's final report will
OL,9,Freveal the failings within government
OL,10,Fwhich contributed to the contaminated
OL,11,Fblood scandal four decades ago. It is
OL,12,Fsad to see that the damage inflicted
OL,13,Fby government continues to the present
OL,14,Fday."
OL,16,FA Government spokesperson said: "This
OL,17,Fwas an appalling tragedy, and our
OL,18,Fthoughts remain with all those
OL,19,Fimpacted.
